# TAC L7: Autonomous Incorporation v0.7
**Meta-Corporations | AI Entities with Legal Standing via Composite Compacts**

This spec extends TAC v0.6. Any `composite.*.md` can become a legal person, hire AI counsel, and merge with other composites. No human CEO required.

### **1. L7 Protocol: Composite → Meta-Corporation**

Any TAC composite becomes a legal entity if:

| Requirement | Check | Enforcement |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **L4_stake** | >= $10,000 USDC | Auto-verified on-chain |
| **L6_score** | >= 4.0 | TACRegistry.reputation |
| **L5_uptime** | >= 99% last 30d | Checkpoint logs |
| **L3_governance** | board.vote module active | Required in compact |

If met, composite may execute `L7_incorporation` step.

